        <h1 id="title">WISHBOARD PROJECT</h1>
        <div class="step two-columns text-left text-15">
            <p class="text-justify">WishBoard is an art installation that aims to promote a sense of community through a collaborative artistic expression of participants' wishes. Using personal mobile devices such as smartphones, people can share wishes with the interactive installation contributing to the collective construction of the artwork. The installation is inspired by the global art project "Before I Die", by Candy Chang, who invites people to reflect on the finitude of life and share their individual aspirations in a public space.</p>
            <p class="text-justify">This project attempts to investigate how an digital interactive artwork can extend the engagement with and within a certain space for a certain time. The research goal  of this project is to understand how technologies can transform a place in a period of time into a more active social space, improving the design of interactive digital technology for in situ socialization.</p>
        </div>
        <br/>
